item.title: CVE-2019-6536|2024-08-04T20:23:21.362Z -- lcds%20-%20le%C3%A3o%20consultoria%20e%20desenvolvimento%20de%20sistemas%20ltda%20me -- laquis%20scada
item.description: Opening a specially crafted LCDS LAquis SCADA before 4.3.1.71 ELS file may result in a write past the end of an allocated buffer, which may allow an attacker to execute remote code in the context of the current process.
